  "texts": [
    "First, the documents and user prompts are converted into a compatible format to perform relevancy search.",
    "Typically this is accomplished by converting the document collection and user prompts into numerical representations using embedding language models.",
    "RAG model architectures compare the embeddings of user prompts within the vector of the knowledge library.",
    "The original user prompt is then appended with relevant context from similar documents within the knowledge library.",
    "This augmented prompt is then sent to the foundation model."
  ],
